CatDescriptText: Joe Garagiola, a well known sports commentator and former St. Louis Cardinals (1946-1954) baseball player, poses with another man for photograph before the July 7, 1959 All Star game at Forbes Field.  In the background the fans fill the stadium seats.  A Chicago Cubs baseball player is in the background to the right.
TitMainTitle: Baseball commentator Joe Garagiola holding camera, standing with unknown man at Forbes Field for 1959 All Star Game
